301
00:16:02,433 --> 00:16:05,033
Schafer: Well, that's a good question.
That's an interesting question.

302
00:16:05,033 --> 00:16:07,933
Gilbert: I'm jumping ahead.
Schafer: We don't know.

303
00:16:07,933 --> 00:16:10,000
Schafer: Mostly I just get this relief
